# Code owners for Mite.
#
# The Bastion reviewer policy and its CI workflow are protected paths: a PR must
# not be able to weaken the gates that judge it or re-point who pays for a
# review. The workflow also carries the per-author subscription billing mapping,
# so changing who may spend a subscription stays a human-reviewed change. Enable
# "Require review from Code Owners" in branch protection for this to bind.
/.bastion.yaml              @jssblck
/.github/workflows/bastion.yml  @jssblck
/.github/CODEOWNERS         @jssblck
